.TH "dwc2_hsotg_ctrl_epint" 9 "dwc2_hsotg_ctrl_epint" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dwc2_hsotg_ctrl_epint \- enable/disable an endpoint irq
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" dwc2_hsotg_ctrl_epint
.BI "(struct dwc2_hsotg *hsotg "  ","
.BI "unsigned int ep "  ","
.BI "unsigned int dir_in "  ","
.BI "unsigned int en "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hsotg" 12
The device state
.IP "ep" 12
The endpoint index
.IP "dir_in" 12
True if direction is in.
.IP "en" 12
The enable value, true to enable
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Set or clear the mask for an individual endpoint's interrupt
request.
